It's bitter goodbyes in this heart-wrenching chapter of Stephen King'sâ€¨apocalyptic epic. Also: What's the trouble with young Leo Rockway?

results.title: The Stand: The Night Has Come (2011) #3
results.description: The dark man's empire is crumbling. A spy is slipping through the cracks, his right-hand man has gone rogue, and now his bride is...what, exactly? It's Nadine's final reckoning with good old Randy Flagg, True Believers, and it will not be for the weak of heart. And as bad as things are in Vegas, they're about to get worse for our quartet of reluctant heroes as they enter the west. They started with four, soon there will only be three...
